Poetry Heals: For a cultural and non-preachy alternative to a church sermon, poet Phiwe Gazu presents an offering of poetry that aims to heal those who hear it. Details: The session takes place on September  21 at the Jazzy Rainbow, 93 Smiso Nkwanyana Road, Durban.
